{
  "id": "adv_card_kkr_52_02",
  "title": "赤崎こころ 2話 ぎいやあああああーっ！",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_photo_themepark-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "themepark-00-000-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gaya-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr001.m4a",
      "text": "おお～！　さすがは大人気の遊園地……\n沢山の人で賑わってますね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Oooh~! As expected of such a popular amusement park…\nIt’s so lively and crowded~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 4.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr002.m4a",
      "text": "ここの遊園地は、人気のアトラクションが沢山あるから\n一度は来ておきたかったんですよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "This amusement park has tons of famous attractions‚\nso I've always wanted to come at least once~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 11.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr003.m4a",
      "text": "なんせ、こころは人気者で忙しいですから\nこの機会を逃すと、次はいつ来られるか分かりませんし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After all‚ Kokoro is so popular and busy~\nIf I miss this chance‚ who knows when I’ll be able to come again.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 17.9,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-koh001.m4a",
      "text": "それはそうだが……まったく\n無理やり引っ張って来るなんて酷いぞ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Well‚ that’s true… but still.\nDragging me here by force is just cruel.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 26.1,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr004.m4a",
      "text": "きっと{user}さんも、最後には楽し過ぎて\n帰りたくない～って泣き叫んでますよ～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I’m sure you‚ {user}-san‚ will be having so much fun~\nYou’ll be crying that you don’t want to go home~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 32.6472333272,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rollercoaster-02.m4a",
          "delay": 3661.7913326000034,
          "startTime": 36.3090246598
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr005.m4a",
      "text": "あ、こころはあのジェットコースターに\n乗りたいです～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Kokoro wants to ride\nthat roller coaster~!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 38.7472333272,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-koh002.m4a",
      "text": "乗客が物凄い悲鳴を上げているんだが……\nあんなスピードで急降下するのか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "The passengers are screaming like crazy though…\nIt drops that fast…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 44.6149505235,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr006.m4a",
      "text": "え？　まさか怖くて乗れないとか言いませんよね？\nどうしても無理だっていうなら、仕方ないですけど～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh? You’re not going to say you’re too scared to ride it‚ right?\nIf it’s absolutely impossible for you‚ then it can’t be helped~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 52.6191381772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr007.m4a",
      "text": "こんなジェットコースターにビビっちゃうなんて\n{user}さんも可愛いところあるんですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Being scared of a roller coaster like this—\n{user}-san‚ you have a cute side too.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.6191381772,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-koh003.m4a",
      "text": "……乗れないなんて言ってないだろ\n仕方ない、せっかく来たんだ。とことん付き合うよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…I never said I couldn’t ride it.\nFine‚ we’re here anyway. I’ll go all the way with you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 65.8666666667,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr008.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、言いましたね？　……いいこと思いつきました\nそれじゃどちらが遊園地を楽しめるか、勝負です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ you said it? …I just got a great idea.\nThen let’s compete to see who enjoys the amusement park more!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 75.1323374749,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr009.m4a",
      "text": "こころが勝負に勝ったら……\nこころをリズノワのセンターにしてもらいます！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "If Kokoro wins…\nyou’ll make Kokoro the center of LizNoir!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 81.7990056675,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-koh004.m4a",
      "text": "それはメンバーみんなで話し合って決めることだろ\n大体、こころが負けたらどうするんだ？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s something the whole group decides together.\nAnd what if you lose?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 88.7333368938,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr010.m4a",
      "text": "その時はこころがリズノワのセンターになってあげます",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then Kokoro will become the center of LizNoir for you.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 91.8108183461,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-koh005.m4a",
      "text": "同じじゃないか……\nそれに、それだと俺の得が全くないんだが",
      "translations": {
        "en": "That’s the same thing…\nAnd that doesn’t benefit me at all.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 98.5000035604,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr011.m4a",
      "text": "いいから早くジェットコースターに乗りましょう\n先に悲鳴を上げて、怖がった方が負けですからね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Enough talking‚ let’s hurry and get on the roller coaster.\nWhoever screams first and gets scared loses~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 105.9930587451,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-koh006.m4a",
      "text": "仕方ないな……せっかくの慰安旅行だし\n付き合ってやるか",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Fine… this is a recreational trip‚ after all.\nI’ll go along with it.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 114.0666646322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rollercoaster-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 116.9244179645
    },
    {
      "type": "sfx",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rollercoaster-02.m4a",
      "startTime": 116.9244179645
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr012.m4a",
      "text": "ぎいやあああああーっ！　なんですかこれ！？\n本格的過ぎるんですけどーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Giiyaaaaaaaah!! What is this!?\nThis is way too intense–!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 121.7975257714,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_rollercoaster-02.m4a",
          "delay": 18882.247281299995,
          "startTime": 136.6
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-koh007.m4a",
      "text": "あっ、こ、こころ、今、悲鳴上げたな？\nこころの負け……うわあーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ Ko–Kokoro‚ you just screamed‚ didn’t you?\nThat means you lose… uwaaah—!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 128.4666646322,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr013.m4a",
      "text": "い、今のは歓喜の叫び声ですから、ノーカンですっ！\n……ぎゃあああーーっ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Th-that was a cry of joy‚ so it doesn’t count!\n…Gyaaaaaaah!!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 137.7249290589,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr014.m4a",
      "text": "はぁ、はぁ……さっきのジェットコースターの勝負は\n……引き分けですね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Haa… haa… regarding the roller coaster match earlier—\n…it’s a draw.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 148.3294534206,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-koh008.m4a",
      "text": "先に悲鳴を上げたのはこころだったけどな\n負けず嫌いもそこまでいくと尊敬するよ……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "You were the one who screamed first‚ though.\nYour stubbornness is almost admirable at this point…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 154.4333277385,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr015.m4a",
      "text": "勝負は次のアトラクションに持ち越しです\n次にこころ達が挑むのは……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Then the match continues with the next attraction!\nThe next thing we’re challenging is…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 161.0520610969,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr016.m4a",
      "text": "泣く子がさらに泣きまくると評判の\n世界最大級にして最恐のお化け屋敷です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Famous for making even crying kids cry even harder—\nthe world’s biggest and scariest haunted house!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 167.4187277635,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-koh009.m4a",
      "text": "えっ……こ、ここのお化け屋敷は\nやめておいた方がいいんじゃないか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Eh… th-the haunted house here—\nmaybe we should avoid it?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 175.2333312989,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr017.m4a",
      "text": "やれやれ、{user}さんまで\n愛ちゃんと同じこと言うんですね～",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Good grief‚ {user}-san‚\neven you are saying the same thing Ai-chan said~",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 180.3956665834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-kkr018.m4a",
      "text": "所詮は遊園地のお化け屋敷ですよ？\nどうせ大したことないですから、行きましょう",
      "translations": {
        "en": "It’s just an amusement park haunted house‚ you know?\nIt won’t be that scary anyway‚ so let’s go.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 186.5956665834,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "koh",
      "speakerName": "{user}",
      "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-makino.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/cardStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02/sud_vo_adv_card_kkr_52_02-koh010.m4a",
      "text": "……このアトラクションの怖い噂\nこころは聞いたことないのか？",
